{"tid":1699693,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民監警]  有冇諗過全民CCTV監警?","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:02:43.000Z","uid":107157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a04307dedb7be4d8742f19ccc94923ec5e821e1","tid":1699693,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"已經太多案件因為冇cctv或者角度唔適合而不了了之，咩都告唔入。<br />\n<br />\n建議全民齊裝cam，<br />\n買啲充電式CCTV搵隱蔽位周街裝。<br />\n啲狗做咩事都無所遁形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近狗屋既裝，高位裝，近海裝，空地裝，甚至屋企裝監視屋外情況。<br />\n裝完映相作証，事後比人拆左就証明到比大家知道死因絕對有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩高招請賜教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再有人被自殺就同我推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd3ece9f547c9cfda4d68607d3176f43d6ea3a","tid":1699693,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警為所欲為<br />\n港人反抗自衛</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"de0a5a190e49744ca0ef28515367b10b0e7ed280","tid":1699693,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民監警，刻不容緩</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"44d882506ca014235390ee72ebe40cc1a5a070b5","tid":1699693,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"大廈天台必經之路裝針孔鏡頭"},{"pid":"11b91b5c4614ecc49397b9e80c4dea28dd6ae023","tid":1699693,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d882506ca014235390ee72ebe40cc1a5a070b5","tid":1699693,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"大廈天台必經之路裝針孔鏡頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:24